Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.65,0:01:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{忍び寄る陰謀}Episode 010\NCreeping conspiracy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.03,0:01:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん。出てってよ。}Ayuhara-san, leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.67,0:01:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ。出て行ってよ。}Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.37,0:01:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{聞こえないの？}Can't you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{ゆりさん。}Yuri-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.48,0:01:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{失礼ですよ、そんな言い方としては。}You're being rude to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.11,0:01:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたは黙ってて。}You shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.50,0:01:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{何よXXX。}What do you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.78,0:01:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉さん、何てこと言うの？お母さんに向かって。}Izumi-san, that's no way to speak to your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.76,0:02:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{お母さんですって？}"Mother", you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.00,0:02:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{フン。}Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.49,0:02:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{とんでもないわ。}What a thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.57,0:02:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{こんな人はお母さんだ何て…}For this woman to be my mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.09,0:02:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{ありがた迷惑だわ。}Thanks but no.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.89,0:02:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{人前だけ良い顔しだって…}She's nice before others.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX何は考えてるか。}But there's no telling what she thinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.90,0:02:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{バカにしないでとか。}She must hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.59,0:02:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉さん！}Izumi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.14,0:02:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.74,0:02:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{何すんのよ？}What are you doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.95,0:02:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{見損なったわ、泉さん。}I've misjudged you, Izumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.51,0:02:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{たって義理の親かでも、親は親じゃないの。}Even if she's your step mom, a parent is a parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.86,0:02:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{それより、あなたは…}You, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{は？もうたくさん。}Huh? I've heard enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.47,0:02:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{あんたなんか…何が分かるもんですか？}What can you possibly know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.38,0:02:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{さっさと帰ってよ。}Hurry up and go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.81,0:02:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{帰ってて言っての、もう分かんないの？}Don't you understand what's said to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{帰らないのね。}Doesn't look so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.80,0:02:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、勝手にするといいわ。}Fine, do whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.26,0:02:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{フン。}Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.12,0:02:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉さん…}Izumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{あの…}Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.83,0:02:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうぞ、今日はこれでお引き取りよ。}Please, let's call it a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.79,0:02:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.72,0:02:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、失礼します。}Well then, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.93,0:02:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.52,0:02:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.42,0:02:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.38,0:02:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま。}My...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.21,0:02:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{それじゃあなた、昨日やっぱり泉さんの家へ(X・行)ったのね。}So you really went to Izumi's home yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:02:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{んん。だけど駄目だったわ。}Yep... but it was no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.37,0:02:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{でしょう？}See?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{だから「止しなさい」と言ったのよ。}That's why I told you to give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.83,0:03:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{良いじゃないの？}Isn't it better this way? {良いじゃないの？}We don't have to care about her anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.00,0:03:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{でもあたしは諦めないわ。}I'm not giving up yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.77,0:03:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{何度でも、説得してみるつもりよ。}I'll persuade her until I succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.58,0:03:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしはXXXと思うわ。}I really admire that side of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.63,0:03:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね。それより、残った人達だけで、何とか頑張るできじゃないかしら？}But her aside, don't you think the others are doing pretty well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{うん。みちろん、それも大切だけど…}They do and I appreciate it. But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{試合に勝つためには、泉さんを絶対欲しい人なのよ。}I'd really like to have Izumi-san on our side in the future matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{それはあなたの買い被りよ。}Don't you overrate her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{(XXX・原因は)あたしたちが楽しそうに勝ったじゃない？}Didn't we win with her the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{大丈夫。}It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.13,0:03:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたとあたしはいれば、絶対よ。}With you and me, it's certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{勝負に絶対なんでXXXない。}There are no certainties in sports.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.74,0:03:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉さんXXX大変間違いだわ。}Letting her go will be a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.37,0:03:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{ー鮎原さん、大変よ。泉さんは陸上部に入ってます。\Nーえ？}- Ayuhara-san, Izumi-san joined the track and field club.\N- Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.04,0:03:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{陸上部って？}Track and field club?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.97,0:03:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうなのよ。}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.83,0:03:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーもうトラックで練習してるわよ。\Nーま。}- She's practicing on the track.\N- Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{ほら、ごらんなさい。}Told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.93,0:03:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{だからいつまでも、「泉さん、泉さん」何て言うことないわよ。}That's why we're better off letting her go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{酷い。}That's low.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{一体泉さんは何を考えてるのかしら？}What the heck were you thinking, Izumi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.45,0:04:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{それにしても、泉さんって冷たいわね。}But Izumi-san sure is cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{人事(XXX・裏)出してくれても良いのに…}She left behind everyone's back...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたし本郷先生に相談してくる。}I'll see professor Hongou for an advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.73,0:04:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{陸上部に入ったことなら、知ってる。}I already know she switched clubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.44,0:04:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.51,0:04:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{ちょっと前に、泉くんからこれが出てるんだ。}Just a while ago, she gave me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.32,0:04:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{《退部届く》\N《泉ゆり》}《Letter of resignation》\N《Izumi Yuri》
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま。じゃ、本郷先生は泉さんの退部を認めたんですか？}Professor, did you accept her resignation then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{や、それは…}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.59,0:04:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{僕だって、認めたくなかった。}I didn't want to accept it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.46,0:04:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{しかし、どうしてもと言われれば、個人の自由を縛るのはいかんね。}But no matter what you say, you can't go against one's free will.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{よい。}Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.23,0:04:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.35,0:04:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉さん。あなたに話があるんだけど。}Izumi-san, we need to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.29,0:04:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{話って何なの？}What about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉さん…あなたはなぜあたしたちに黙って、陸上部になんか入ったのよ？}Why did you keep it from us and leave the club on your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{水臭いよ、泉さん。}That wasn't cool, Izumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.49,0:04:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたちは四天王とかなんとか言われて、昨日まで一緒にやってきた仲間じゃない。}Big Four or not, we did everything together until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.57,0:04:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレー部を辞めるんなら、辞めるって…なぜ人事言ってくれないの？}Why didn't you talk to us about quitting the volleyball club?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.95,0:05:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{言ったて無駄だって思ってからよ。}It wouldn't change anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.95,0:05:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{あんたたちこそ、何よ？}Besides what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{あんな鮎原さんの子分成って…}After flocking to Ayuhara-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.04,0:05:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{良くそんな平気で居られるわね。}You have some nerve saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.05,0:05:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{待って、泉さん。}Just a second, Izumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.29,0:05:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたちだって最初は辞めるつもりで退部届も書いたわ。}At first we wanted to quit the club too, and wrote our own resignation letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.03,0:05:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも結局辞められなかったわ。}But in the end we couldn't quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレーが好きだからよ。}We love volleyball after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレーが離れて、あたしたちに一枚はないわ。}Besides volleyball, we don't have anything special.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉さんだって、そんなはずじゃないの？}Doesn't it apply to you too, Izumi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.42,0:05:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{だからって。}Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{あの人の下についてまでやりたくないわ。}I don't want to be under that girl's thumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.77,0:05:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{あんたたちのその奴隷根性Xあたしには止まれなくいやなのよ。}If you want to be her lackeys so much, I won't stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{汚いわよ。何よ。}How worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.91,0:05:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{奴隷根性ですって？}"Lackeys", you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.45,0:05:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{失礼なこと言わないで。}Don't be rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.80,0:05:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたこそ、何よ。}What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.03,0:05:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{いつまでも詰まらないことにこだわって…}You used to fret over silliest things...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{…僻み根性も大概にするといいわ？}...but now you think cynicism is cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.22,0:05:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうよ。勝手にいなさいよ。}Yeah. Do whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.59,0:05:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{絶交だわ。}We're through.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.12,0:05:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{これで何もかもお終いだわ。}This might be the end of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.89,0:05:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、泉さんは本郷先生にも退部の理由を言わなかったの？}So Izumi-san didn't tell professor Hongou why she resigned?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.16,0:05:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{酷い人ね。これ(XXX・から後負け犬の)ついたでしょう？}That's harsh. She ought to do this much alone, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.55,0:05:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{んん。だけど、あれほどバレーボールを好きな泉さんは…}Hmm... but Izumi-san, who likes volleyball this much...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.39,0:05:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレーを辞めて、陸上部に入れ、決心するには何が理由がはずよ。}She must have had a good reason to join the track and field club.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.11,0:05:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね？そうでしょう？}Don't you think so too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{そんな…泉さんのこと何かもうどうでも良いじゃん？}Why don't we forget about her already?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.26,0:06:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{それより、明後日からの試合のこと考えましょう。}Instead let's think about the nearing matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{あら？}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.69,0:06:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね、ちょっと、あれ見て。泉さんじゃない？}Hey, look, isn't it Izumi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.44,0:06:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.06,0:06:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま、努さんの一緒よ。}Whoa, she's with Tsutomu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.01,0:06:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{これが一体どう言うことなんだろう…}I wonder what's the meaning of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.36,0:06:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうして努くんと泉さんは一緒に…}Why Tsutomu-kun and Izumi-san are together?...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.57,0:06:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{お？}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.52,0:06:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{努くん。}Tsutomu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.82,0:06:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{なんだ、君か？}What, it's just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.11,0:06:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうしたの？}What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.09,0:06:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたを待てたのよ。}I've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{僕を？}For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.20,0:06:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{ちょっと努くんに聞きたいこと成って…}There's something I want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.71,0:06:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{聞きたいことって何だ？}What do you want to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.37,0:06:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉さんのことなんだけど。}It's about Izumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.83,0:06:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{努くん何時から泉さんと付き合いXになったの？}Tsutomu-kun, for how long are you going out with Izumi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.77,0:06:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{何時からって…}How long I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{彼女の家が同じ方向だから、良く帰りに一緒に成るだけだよ。}Her home is in the same direction as mine, so we go home together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.40,0:06:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{それがどうかしたのか？}Something wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.66,0:07:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたし…泉さんて人を分からんくなっちゃったのよ。}I... don't think I can understand Izumi-san any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、あの人はバレー部を辞めたことか。}Ah, it's about her quitting the club, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{それなら、僕も心配してたんだ。}I'm worried about that too, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{なんとか、仲良くやれないものがってね。}It seems you two just can't get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしは努力したわ。}I tried to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.65,0:07:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、あの人は全然あたしの言うこと何か聞いてくれないで…}But she has no intention of listening to what I'm saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.77,0:07:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{一方的に辞めちゃったのよ。}...and quit the club just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.69,0:07:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、泉くんには人に言えない苦しい事情があるんだろう。}But Izumi-san's situation is very tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{仕方ないよ。}You can't blame her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.44,0:07:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま、随分同情的ね。}Wow, you sympathize with her a lot, don't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.60,0:07:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうして？}Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.74,0:07:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうしてと言われても、困るけど。}Why shouldn't I be sympathetic?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.81,0:07:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{可笑しいわ。変よ。}It's weird. Suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{おい、待ってよ。何が変なんだよ？}Wait, hold on! What do you mean by "suspicious"!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{何なんだ？}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.40,0:07:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{だって…努くんたら…あたしの苦しみ何て、これっぽっちも組んでくれないで、泉さんの肩ばかり持つんですよ。}Tsutomu-kun, when I'm in trouble, you don't move the slightest... but for Izumi-san, you grab her shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.02,0:07:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{バカなこと言うな。}Don't say stupid things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.31,0:07:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{そんな言い方するなんて、君らしくないぜ。}It's not like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.53,0:07:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうせあたしはバカよ。}Excuse me for being stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.12,0:07:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーこうぜちゃん。\Nー知らない！}- Kozue-chan!\N- Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{《春季全国中学バレーボール選手権大会東海地区予選トーナメント近い!!》}The Toukai district qualifiers for the spring All-Japan Middle School Volleyball Tournament are near!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.18,0:07:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.92,0:07:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーそれ。\Nーはい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.54,0:07:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:07:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい、はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.20,0:07:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.26,0:07:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{ぁあい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.40,0:07:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{えい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい、皆。}Hey, girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.63,0:08:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{練習を止め、集まってくれ。}Stop and come here for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.20,0:08:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーはい！\Nーはい！}- Yes sir!\N- Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{よし、集まったな。}Okay, you're gathered.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.36,0:08:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{良いか、皆。}Listen, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.39,0:08:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{いよいよ明日から全国大会の地区予選が始まる。}At last, the district qualifiers for the All-Japan Tournament start tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.00,0:08:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{トーナメントだから、一度負ければ、それは終わりだ。}It's a tournament, so one loss and we're out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.70,0:08:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXXぞ。}You get what it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.98,0:08:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{優勝できるかどうかは…}Whether we can win or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{…皆が今までに練習で身につけた実力を…}...depends on the skills you gathered in the training...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.15,0:08:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{…百パーセント出せるかどうかに勝ってるんだ。}...and whether you use them at 100% in the matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.61,0:08:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{もし皆が実力を出しきれば…}If you go all out...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.93,0:08:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{地区代表はもちろん…}...the qualifications...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.39,0:08:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{全国大会でも優勝できるだろう。}...and, of course, the tournament, are within our reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.58,0:08:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{皆…}Girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.27,0:08:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{頑張ってくれよ！}Give it your all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.10,0:08:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーはい。\Nーはい。}- Yes sir!\N- Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{良いな？}Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.97,0:08:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{わが富士見学園の名門にかけて…}Let's prove our Fujimi's prestige...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{何が何でもか勝ち抜くんだ。}...and win through at any cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.23,0:08:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーはい！\Nーはい。頑張ります。}- Yeah!\N- Yes, we'll work hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.89,0:08:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{よし。}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.32,0:08:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{最後の仕上げだ。練習を初め！}Finishing touch! Resume the training!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.84,0:08:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーはい！\Nーはい。}Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.82,0:08:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.59,0:08:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{強い！}So strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.19,0:08:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.15,0:08:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{えい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.56,0:08:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{何だ、何だ！}What's that, what's that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.35,0:08:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{しっかりしろ、柏木！}Get a grip, Kashiwagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.61,0:08:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXXトーナメントにXXXいけんぞ。}You won't have time in the tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.49,0:08:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーすみません。\Nー取れ！}- I'm sorry!\N- Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.07,0:08:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.99,0:08:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{次！}Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.78,0:08:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{行くぞ。}Here it goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.56,0:08:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.28,0:08:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{取れ！}Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:08:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:08:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{よぉ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.42,0:08:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.68,0:09:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.26,0:09:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{行くぞ。}More!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.57,0:09:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{よし、次！}Okay, next!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.32,0:09:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{アタックコンビ！}Attack duo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.13,0:09:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.71,0:09:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.14,0:09:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{覚えてらっしゃい。}Mark my words.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.26,0:09:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{絶対優勝何かさせないから。}I won't let you win at any rate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{あら、泉さん。}Ah, Izumi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.99,0:09:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{こんな所で…何やってるのよ？}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.09,0:09:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{皆練習してんのよ。}We're practicing now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.89,0:09:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.46,0:09:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたし、今日休むわ。}I took a day off today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.64,0:09:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{休む？}A day off?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{そんな勝手なことって…ある？}Out of the blue like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.89,0:09:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{駄目よ。陸上部入った、陸上部のやり方にしXXなきゃ。}You can't... when you're in our club, you need to be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.37,0:09:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、あたし…}See...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.34,0:09:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{今日は弱るからお先に失礼するわ。}I feel ill today. I'm going home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.20,0:09:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉さん！駄目よ！}Izumi-san! You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.48,0:09:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、XXX。}Ah, that felt good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.61,0:09:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。良いわね、ちょっと。}Yes, just a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.44,0:09:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{でもさ…}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.20,0:09:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{いよいよ明日からXXXなるわ！}The qualifiers start tomorrow. I'm excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.42,0:09:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{最初に当たるのは…川北中学ね。}Our first opponent is Kawakita Middle School.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.97,0:09:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{勝って、勝って、勝ち抜くだけよ。}Let's win, win, win all the way through!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーえ。\Nーえ。}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.38,0:09:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{頑張りましょう。}Let's work hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.89,0:09:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、あたし早く東海に行きたいわ。}Ah, I want to see Toukai already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:10:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{皆、驚くわよ。今まで出ると負けの富士見学園の地区代表に選ばれたら…}I'm surprised though - Fujimi's been losing all this time and now we enter district qualifiers...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{《教員室》}《Teachers room》
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.15,0:10:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ…}Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.92,0:10:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{優勝は間違いないね。}We'll win for sure, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.59,0:10:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{と思います。}...I think so, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.44,0:10:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{思うだけじゃ困るよ、本郷先生。}Thinking won't get us far, professor Hongou.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{は。}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.10,0:10:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{や、しかし…}However,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.02,0:10:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{勝負は水物ですから。}a match is like water.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.48,0:10:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{やってみないことには(分かりません・図りません)。}You can't know the outcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{え、いかんいかん。コーチのあんたそんなに自身のないことじゃん。}It's no good. The coach having no confidence is a bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.87,0:10:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうですよ、本郷先生。}That's right, professor Hongou.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.94,0:10:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{大体ですよ。}Furthermore...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.23,0:10:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{自分はコーチすれば、絶対優勝さしてみせるってXXXは、え？あなたなんですからね。}Who promised a dazzling victory if they became a coach, hm? Wasn't that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.89,0:10:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。}Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{もちろん、そのつもりです。}My intention didn't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.67,0:10:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{だったらね、約束通り優勝して見せてくださいよ。}Then give us a dazzling victory you promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.06,0:10:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉ゆりほどの優秀な戦士のタイプを認める以上…}Although I think you'll be hard pressed...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.41,0:10:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{とは十分に自身が終わりなんでしょうな。}...to find an excellent warrior such as Izumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{しかし、先生。}But professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.77,0:10:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉ゆりのタイプは…本人の個人的な理由に依るもんですから。}Players like Izumi are in it for themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.51,0:10:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ。それはどうかな。}Well, I wonder about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.85,0:10:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{チームワークは大切とか何とか言いながら、退部ゴタゴタしてるようじゃないんですから。}While you were preaching about teamwork and whatnot, she quit your club nonetheless.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.02,0:10:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{へ？違いますか？}Am I not right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.07,0:10:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{いえ。}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.73,0:10:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{大丈夫です。}It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.78,0:10:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{ご心配には及びません。}You don't need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.03,0:10:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうですか。}Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:11:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{ならいいんですからね。}Very well, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.66,0:11:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{又私にバレー部へ戻ってくれ何て泣きついてこないようにくれぐれも頼みますよ、本郷先生。}But don't come to me crying and begging to get her back in your club, professor Hongou.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{分かってます。}I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.95,0:11:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{明日からの試合でその答えが出るはずです。}Watch us in the matches from tomorrow on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.20,0:11:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{思い出すわ。}How nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.69,0:11:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたちは良く喧嘩したのね。}We used to fight so much, didn't we.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.92,0:11:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうね。}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.80,0:11:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、そのおかげで、あたしたち仲良しになれたんじゃない？}But we became friends thanks to it, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.49,0:11:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{そう言えば、あの頃のあたしって…}Now that you say it, I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.44,0:11:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうして捻くれてたのかしら。}...why I rebelled so much back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉さんほどじゃないわ。}Not unlike Izumi-san, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま、ふふ。}My, hehe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{ちょっと見て。}Check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.24,0:11:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、努くんと泉さんよ。}Ah, Tsutomu-kun and Izumi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{なくなく。}Sniffle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.65,0:11:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉くん。}Izumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま！}Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{ショック！}What a shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.28,0:11:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{可笑しいは、あの二人。}They're acting weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.67,0:11:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{勇気過ぎよ。}They're too bold!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{中学生として、あんな態度を取るべきじゃないわよね。}It's unbecoming for middle schoolers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.50,0:11:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{努さんも努さんよ。}Tsutomu-san's Tsutomu-san, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.14,0:11:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{あの泉さんなんかと不潔だわ。}What he's doing with Izumi-san... how filthy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.70,0:11:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{こんなことが学校に知れたら、それこそは大変よ。}If the school finds out, they'll be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:12:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、もう泣くの止せよ。}Come on, stop crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.97,0:12:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{人に見られたら、変に思われずね。}If people saw us, they'd jump to conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{いいの。}I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX}I just can't take it any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.84,0:12:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{そんなやけをお越し駄目だよ。}Don't feel down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.99,0:12:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{冷静に成るんだ。ね、泉くん？}Stay calm, okay, Izumi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.32,0:12:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね？}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.28,0:12:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね、泉くん。}Hey, Izumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.90,0:12:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま。もうこれ以上は許せないわ。}Wow. I can't stay out of this any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.87,0:12:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうよ。行って忠告してあげなきゃ。}Yeah. Let's give them a warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.89,0:12:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ。涙を拭いて。}Wipe your tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたたち。}You two.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.91,0:12:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{お。}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.49,0:12:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{こずえちゃん。}Kozue-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.59,0:12:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{努くん、何してるの、こんな所で。}Tsutomu-kun, what are you two doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.60,0:12:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{見たのはあたしたちだけだから、いいけど、もし他の人に見られたらどうするのよ？}It'd be okay if only us saw you, but what if you were seen by other people?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.97,0:12:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{軽蔑するわ、努さん。}They'll disdain you, Tsutomu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.80,0:12:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{違うよ。変な誤解をしないでくれよ。}You got it all wrong! Don't say weird things!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.15,0:12:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま。まぁ、涼しい。}Whoa, how cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.30,0:12:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{誤解をしないでくれもないでしょう。}It's too late to call it a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{一体何してたのよ、こんな所で。}What were you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.10,0:12:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{何をしようと大きなお世話よ。}What a thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.86,0:12:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{あんたたちには、何も関係ないことよ。}It's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.82,0:13:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{黙ってて。}Keep your mouths shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.83,0:13:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{フン。}Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{何ですって！}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.17,0:13:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{あんたたちこそ、何よ。}What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.75,0:13:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{変な目で見て…}Gawking at us like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.71,0:13:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{間、話を聞いてくれよ。鮎原くん、早川くん。}Hey, listen for a bit, Ayuhara-kun, Hayakawa-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.26,0:13:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{実は、泉くんは…}Actually, Izumi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.55,0:13:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{止めて。}Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも…}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.35,0:13:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{無駄よ。}It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.28,0:13:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{こんな人達に何を話したった駄目よ。分かるもんですか。}There's no talking to these girls. There's no way they'd understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.98,0:13:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{まあ、失礼ね。}How rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.38,0:13:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉さん。あなたこそ、どうしたのよ。}Izumi-san, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.49,0:13:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたちに負けたからって、バレー部を逃がすなんて…卑怯じゃない？}Quitting the club after losing to us... that's cowardice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.89,0:13:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{負けたですって？}Lost, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.30,0:13:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{フン。}Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.88,0:13:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXXよ。}Don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.79,0:13:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしは本当に負けたと思ってんの？}Do you really think I've lost to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.09,0:13:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{負けたじゃない？}What was it then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.25,0:13:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{嘘だって言うなら、何度でもお相手はするわよ。}If you think you won, feel free to take us on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.14,0:13:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{何とでも言いなさいよ。}Say what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.48,0:13:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしの抜けたバレー部なんて…}The club I parted with...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{全然勝つみたいなもんじゃないの。}...in my eyes, didn't win at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.23,0:13:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま。}Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.94,0:13:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉くん。}Izumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.02,0:13:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたし無に予選で優勝できるとでも思ってんの？}Do you really think you can win the qualifiers without me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.79,0:13:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{優勝しますとも。}We'll win all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉さん。重い違いしないで。}Izumi-san. Don't make a big mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたちはあなたにバレー部に残ってもらいたいからこそ、こんなこと言うのよ。}We're saying this precisely because we want you back in our club.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.24,0:13:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{嘘！}Don't lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.12,0:14:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{心の中じゃあたがいなくなって、せいせいしたと思ってるくせに分かってるわよ。}At heart, you're happy that I'm no longer there! I understand that much!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.62,0:14:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX、泉くん。}Calm down, Izumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{こうぜちゃん。}Kozue-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.26,0:14:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉くんは…ね…}Izumi-kun was... see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.88,0:14:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{止めてXX止めて！}I told you not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{しかし…}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{いいのよ。それより…}It's okay. At any rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.80,0:14:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{明日から試合を楽しみに拝見するわ。}I'm looking forward to the upcoming matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.68,0:14:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{どんなXXなんか。}And how will you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.89,0:14:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{たっぷり見せてもらうわね。}I'll be watching you very closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.30,0:14:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ。}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.97,0:14:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{お…}Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{待てよ泉くん。}Wait, Izumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.89,0:14:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{努くん、話して。}Tsutomu-kun, say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.31,0:14:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{一体泉さんとなんな話をしてたの？}What have you two talked about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.10,0:14:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{そ、それは…その…つまり…}That's... err... see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.65,0:14:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{いや。やっぱり止そう。}Nah. I really can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.27,0:14:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうしても知りたければ、泉くん自身の口から聞いてくれよ。}If you really need to know, get Izumi-san to say it herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.18,0:14:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{そう。}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.82,0:14:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、良いわ。}All right then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.03,0:14:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{プライベートなことは聞かないことにするわ。}I won't ask about private things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、このままじゃ…}But at this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.68,0:14:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしは気持ちが吹っ切りしないわ。}...I won't be able to get over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.03,0:14:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{とにかく。}Anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.86,0:14:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{これだけははっきりておくよ。}I can say this much:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{僕と泉くんは絶対に何でもない。}There's nothing between me and Izumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.16,0:14:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{そんな下らないこと心配するより…}Rather than worrying about such things,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{明日からお試合に勝つだけを考えろよ。}...better focus on the upcoming matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.65,0:14:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.69,0:14:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{僕も応援に行くよ。}I'll come and cheer you on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.85,0:14:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{本当？}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.70,0:14:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。本当さ。}Yep. Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.51,0:15:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{君達の「木の葉落とし」のサーブを見るのは楽しみにだもな。}I'm looking forward to seeing your "Leaf Fall" serving technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.94,0:15:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{頑張れよ。}Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.02,0:15:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{ありがとう。頑張るわ。}Thanks. We will.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.51,0:15:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも…}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.06,0:15:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{どう考えても、泉さんとあなたのこと…}I can't help but think about you and Izumi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.65,0:15:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{気に成るわ。}I'm really concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.81,0:15:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{そのうちに分かるさ。}You'll understand eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.33,0:15:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{僕を信じてくれよ。}Please have faith in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.99,0:15:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{それはあたしだって、信じたいよ。}Well, I want to, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.62,0:15:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{だけどね。}But... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.90,0:15:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{もう止しましょう、みどりさん。}Let's drop it, Midori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.87,0:15:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{それより、明日から地区予選は始まるのよ。}More importantly, district qualifiers start tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.31,0:15:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{ここまで来たら、すべて忘れて、試合にぶつからなきゃ。}We came this far. Let's forget it all that and focus on the games.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{《東海地区中学バレーボール予選会場》}《Toukai district middle school volleyball qualifying venue》
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.53,0:15:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{《ガンバレ川北中学》}《Good luck, Kawakita Middle School》
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{《必勝！富士見学園》}《Certain victory, Fujimi Academy》
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.02,0:15:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{頑張れよ！}Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.43,0:15:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{えい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.71,0:15:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{良いぞ！}Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.73,0:15:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.89,0:16:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.45,0:16:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーそれ！\Nーはい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.54,0:16:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ！}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.85,0:16:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.58,0:16:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.88,0:16:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{あぁ…！}Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{任して！}Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.65,0:16:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい！}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.03,0:16:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.68,0:16:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.73,0:16:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{お願い！}Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.57,0:16:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい！}Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX}Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.67,0:16:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.13,0:16:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーはい！\Nーああ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.66,0:16:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{良いわよ！}Good, good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.07,0:16:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ！}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.88,0:16:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{負けるもんか！}We won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.52,0:16:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、行っちゃう。}Heave ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.61,0:17:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい！}
