Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.91,0:17:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{よし。}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.55,0:17:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、この調子で行こう。}Let's keep this pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.78,0:17:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{今度そう甘くないわよ。}Next time it won't be this easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{富士見中・曽根中}《Fujimi ・ Sone》
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.24,0:17:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{かかってこい！}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX}Keep it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.32,0:17:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{皆しっかり！}Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.35,0:17:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{勝ってきましょう。}Let's end this fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX}Full focus!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.36,0:17:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.27,0:17:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.97,0:17:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.10,0:17:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{ドンマイドンマイ！}Don't mind, don't mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.37,0:17:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、も一本いただきましょう。ほらほらほら！}All right, one more! Come on come on come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.82,0:17:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{え…}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.83,0:18:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{あぁぁぁ。}Ahh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.46,0:18:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{良いぞ！}- Here I go!\N- Fast, fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.03,0:18:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.87,0:18:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.36,0:18:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。}Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.80,0:18:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{ほら。}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.50,0:18:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{可笑しいわ。}It's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{今日はなぜこんなにXXXかしら？}Why do we struggle so much today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.24,0:18:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{タイム！}Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうした、皆。}What's wrong, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.39,0:18:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{しっかりしてくれよ。}Pull yourself together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.60,0:18:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{昨日のなぜて、まるで違うよ。}It's completely different from yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.96,0:18:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうなんです。}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.17,0:18:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{なぜとか分かりません。}But we don't understand why.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.52,0:18:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{けど調子が出ないんです。}We just can't get through.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.53,0:18:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{いいか。}Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.37,0:18:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{第二セット落とした、不味いぞ。}It'll be bad if we lose the second set.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.00,0:18:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{落ち着いて。いっきゅういっきゅう、丁寧に打ち。}Calm down and strike carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.39,0:18:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{確実に受ける。}Receive precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.82,0:18:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{いいな？}Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.50,0:18:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーはい。\Nーはい。}- Yes.\N- Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.73,0:18:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、やるわよ。}Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.51,0:18:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、頑張って！}Get it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{挽回よ。}It's our come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.29,0:18:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.88,0:18:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.58,0:18:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.11,0:18:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.72,0:18:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.66,0:18:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.93,0:18:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{よし。}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.25,0:19:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{しかし、変だ。}But it's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.65,0:19:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{急にうまくなるわけがないのに…}Suddenly we can't get anywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.48,0:19:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{こっちの欠点分かり、出ない打つされて、苦戦している。}...and they put up a fierce fight exploiting our weak points.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.83,0:19:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{可笑しい。}Strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.92,0:19:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{何があるぞ。これは。}Something's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.01,0:19:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.75,0:19:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.82,0:19:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{ほら、頑張ってのよ！}You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.63,0:19:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{は！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.39,0:19:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{はぁい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.36,0:19:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ見て！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.61,0:19:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{良いぞ、良いぞ！}Good going, good going!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.86,0:19:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{やっと勝てたわ。}We made it after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.40,0:19:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{ゆっくり試合XXX}Good we managed to stay focused.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.05,0:19:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{あら？}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.61,0:19:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉さんも来てるわ？}Izumi-san came after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.75,0:19:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたと言ってただけど…}Although we had such a fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{やっぱりあたしたちの合いにきてくれたのかしら。}In the end she stayed true to her words.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{そう言えば、変なことがあったの。}By the way, something weird happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.70,0:19:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？変なことって？}Hm? Weird how?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.17,0:19:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{うん。泉さんのことよ。}Well, it's about Izumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.06,0:19:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.59,0:19:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{彼女がどうかしたの？}Something's up with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.04,0:19:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{ん。それがね…}Yeah. Wait till you hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.53,0:20:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたし、昨日駅前の喫茶店へ…曽根中学としてと一緒に泉さんは入ってくとこ見たのよ。}I went yesterday to the coffee shop before the station... and I saw her with the girls from Sone Middle School.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{ー可笑しいと思うわない？\Nーえ？}- Strange, don't you think?\N- Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.88,0:20:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{本当！}Very!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.88,0:20:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{それじゃ、今(XXX・大成した相手)じゃないの…}It's the school we're playing against now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.46,0:20:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{ん…どうしてそんなことしたのか知らないけど…}Well, I don't know why she did this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{試合するXXXなんて…ちょっと可笑しくない？}...but meeting with your match opponents is bizarre, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.52,0:20:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{可笑しいわね。}It truly is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.33,0:20:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{一体なんな話おしたのかしら。}What they talked about, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.27,0:20:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{まさか、そんな…}It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.70,0:20:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{いくら泉さんでも…そんな酷いこと…}Even Izumi-san wouldn't do such thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.93,0:20:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉さんは曽根中学の人ともしかしたら…}I hope I'm wrong about Izumi-san and Sone Middle School...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.39,0:20:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{でもそんなこと…}But I can't shake it off...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.70,0:20:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{一体これはどうしたすんな？}- What the heck was that?\N- Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.13,0:20:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{駄目だ、駄目だ！}No good, no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.29,0:20:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{今日みたいな調子では…}With today's performance...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.66,0:20:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{優勝所か地区代表ももう使えないぞ。}...we won't be able to win the qualifiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.32,0:20:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{明日はいよいよ決勝だ。}Tomorrow's the decisive match.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.90,0:20:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{対戦相手は…東海中学だ。}The opponent is Toukai Middle School.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.85,0:21:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{今までの相手とは違う。}They're different from the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.08,0:21:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{余程(XXX・使命で)いけなければ、君が勝てないぞ。}If you don't improve greatly, you'll lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.43,0:21:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、これから二時間の特訓をする。}All right. Two hours of intensive training.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.92,0:21:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{良いな？}Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.55,0:21:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{ー分かりました。\Nーはい！}Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.49,0:21:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{へ…がっくりこんだ。}How depressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.07,0:21:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{もうくたくただわ。}I'm exhausted...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{何？}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.32,0:21:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{工藤！香取！}Kudou! Katori!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.11,0:21:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{お前出ろ。}Step out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.09,0:21:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{お前たちは今すぐXXXを外す！}Leave immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.33,0:21:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{へ？せー先生！…}- Eh?\N- Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.60,0:21:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{明日は池崎と中沢は入れ。}Tomorrow, Ikezaki and Nakazawa will go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.88,0:21:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{良いな？}Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.59,0:21:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい！}Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.65,0:21:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{よし。}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.27,0:21:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{では始める。}Let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.00,0:21:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{かかれ！}Dismissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.71,0:21:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい！}Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.37,0:21:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.89,0:21:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{よし。いけ！}All right, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.87,0:21:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.60,0:21:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.31,0:21:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.06,0:21:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.07,0:21:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.72,0:21:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.33,0:21:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.07,0:21:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.33,0:21:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.73,0:21:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.92,0:21:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.51,0:21:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{はぁい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.45,0:21:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.06,0:21:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{それにしても、予選で苦戦するとはいないな。}But we sure don't need a hard fight in the qualifiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.22,0:21:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{所で、どうくるってきたのか。}I wonder how it'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.65,0:21:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{可笑しい。}Weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:21:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{何があるんだわ。}Something's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.71,0:21:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしは抜けたバレー部何て…勝つみたいなもん。}The club I parted with in my eyes didn't win at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.18,0:22:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたし無で予選に優勝できるとでも思ってるの？}Do you really think you can win the qualifiers without me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.83,0:22:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{ゆっくりXXX。}I'll be watching you very closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.78,0:22:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうだ。そうに違いないわ。}That's it. That must be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.65,0:22:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{《バレー部部室》}《Volleyball club's room》
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.04,0:22:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{お先に。}I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.66,0:22:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{さようなら。}Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.88,0:22:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、小沢さん、待って。}Ah, Ozawa-san, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.44,0:22:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.80,0:22:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{何？}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.00,0:22:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね、小沢さん。}Hey, Ozawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.07,0:22:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{昨日泉さんがいたってお店あたしも一緒に連れてってくれない？ね？}Can you take me to the coffee shop where you saw Izumi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.54,0:22:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{へ？あの喫茶店？}Eh? That shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.44,0:22:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{いいでしょう？}How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.52,0:22:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{うん。それは構わないけど、コーヒー飲みなら、もっと美味しいよ店が…}No biggie. But I know better coffee shops.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.91,0:22:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{ううん。いいのよ。}Nah. It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.51,0:22:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{ちょっと考えがあるの。}I'm curious about this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.50,0:22:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん！私も連れてって。}Ayuhara-san! I want to go too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.67,0:22:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま、みどりさん。}Hey, Midori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.00,0:22:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{えへへ。}Ehehe!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.00,0:22:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{駄目よ。ちゃんと分かってもんだから。}You won't fool me. I figured it out fair and square.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.91,0:22:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{へ？分けってなんなの？}Eh? What was that about figuring it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.36,0:22:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{今に分かるわ。}You'll see it in a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.78,0:23:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{何？}See what?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.22,0:23:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{見ててごらんなさい。}You'll see for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.34,0:23:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{きっと現れるから。}I'm sure they'll show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.40,0:23:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{だれが？}Who will?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.58,0:23:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉さんよ。}Izumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.92,0:23:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{へ？}Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.96,0:23:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{やっぱりそうなのね。}Just as expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.18,0:23:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしの考えが違ってなければね。}Well, that's only if my hunch is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.29,0:23:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、東海中学の人を連れて…？}So she'll bring in Toukai girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.71,0:23:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうよ。}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.00,0:23:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{今日の曽根中学は初対戦のくせにあたしたち…}Even though it was Sone's first match today...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.16,0:23:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{得に香取や工藤の弱点の弱点を…驚く程よく知ってたわ。}...they knew our weak points very well. Especially Katori-san and Kudou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.51,0:23:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま。}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.48,0:23:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、泉さんは敵にスパイしてたってわけ？}So Izumi-san was spying for the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.55,0:23:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{し。}Ssh.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.20,0:23:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{来た。}They're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.52,0:23:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{やっぱり東海中学の人として一緒に来たわ。}She really did contact with Toukai girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.55,0:23:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉ゆりは決勝戦の相手チーム、東海中学バレー部員と一緒にやってきた。}Izumi Yuri brings in the Toukai Middle School volleyball team scheduled for the final game.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.85,0:23:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{やはり泉はスパイなのか。}Was Izumi really a spy all along?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.64,0:24:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{こずえとみどりは怒りにXXX震わせた。}Kozue and Midori tremble with anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.23,0:24:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{さて、東海中学との決勝戦。}The match with Toukai begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.75,0:24:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{前日は(XXX・新た決戦した)富士見学園は打って変わり}Fujimi Academy has changed completely since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.72,0:24:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{(XXX・性急)をきったより猛攻が爆発。}Patience snaps and a fierce attack unleashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.98,0:24:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{こずえのアタックは一息XXX。}Kozue's attack shines brightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.28,0:24:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{一方、応援席で一人離れて座っている泉は…}Meanwhile, Izumi, sitting alone in the audience chair...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.62,0:24:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{ギラギラと憎しみ眼差しでコートのこずえを睨んでいた。}...watches the girls with a glaring hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.85,0:24:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、来週のアタックナンバーワンをお楽しみに。}Please look forward to the next episode.
